# Version control required

This plugin is tracked at `https://github.com/Anush-Prabhu/Formidable-List-View-WP-Plugin.git`.

## After every code change

1. Work only inside `wp-content/plugins/formidable-list-view/`.
2. When a task is complete, **commit** all related changes (do not leave work uncommitted).
3. **Push** to `origin/master` unless the user asks not to push.

## Commit workflow

- Run `git status`, `git diff`, and `git log -1` before committing.
- Write a concise message focused on **why** (Conventional Commits style when it fits).
- Bump `FLV_VERSION` in `formidable-list-view.php` when user-facing behavior or assets change.
- Never commit secrets (`.env`, credentials, `wp-config.php`).

## Do not

- Finish a task with uncommitted plugin changes.
- Skip git because the change is "small".
- Force-push to `master` unless explicitly requested.

## Remote

```text
origin → https://github.com/Anush-Prabhu/Formidable-List-View-WP-Plugin.git
branch → master
```
